ecb033","tid":364782,"uid":27616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:53:53.000Z","msg":"上呀"},{"pid":"de5129865fb1c51ee618065e50fbc1126ccb236c","tid":364782,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T16:58:46.000Z","msg":"每場賽事每收到10票,將會捐出$0.1到慈善機構,就算唔夠10票,都會將總票數合併,多出既仙不論多少一律會作新既一毫計算<br />\n<br />\n善款會喺結算後於歇冬期及賽季結束後各捐出一次,希望大家參與同時,仲可以做埋善事,一舉兩得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/347368/page/1</a><br />\nclick入上址即可參閱上半季詳盡賽程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/363474\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/363474</a><br />\n與此同時,LIHKG香港女神總會盃非聯賽參賽女神提名亦都已經展開,截止提名期為17年9月4日0時<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12f56b0ebfdef3f7a50711054c10af8c1496e652","tid":364782,"uid":114678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:06:55.000Z","msg":"你好"},{"pid":"b2d2d32582f6aa9f91b9206c1d210bdcc12b04c3","tid":364782,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:17:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你好</blockquote><br />\n你好"},{"pid":"af594ae0b9683f5f4cb2ae4ee3c716d348464957","tid":364782,"uid":137470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:18:33.000Z","msg":"Hi"},{"pid":"02b7521b65ae60c2411177db5e9901317027d1c9","tid":364782,"uid":22869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-18T17:21:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你好</blockquote><br />\n你好</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要公平,巴打下次等投票完晒先留名啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73